'''Nilgaard Bioprocessing''' was a mining company in the [[Nilgaard sector/Legends|Nilgaard sector]] that established a large plant on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Reaper's World/Legends|Reaper's World]] c. [[3000 BBY]]. Over the years, the world was slowly drained of resources and left barren. With the world stripped of value, Nilgaard Bioprocessing moved their business into the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]].

